OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,FA former police officer who served on
OL,7,Fthe frontline in Belfast for more than
OL,8,F20 years has spoken frankly about the
OL,9,Ftoll the job has taken on his mental
OL,10,Fhealth.
OL,12,FThe 50-year-old, who doesn't want to
OL,13,Fbe identified, took ill health
OL,14,Fretirement in 2023 after being
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with complex PTSD.
OL,17,FHe first joined the PSNI up for the
OL,18,Fchallenge - but left feeling the job
OL,19,Fhad taken a 'good part of him away'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
