OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,FHe was first on the scene when 15-year-
OL,7,Fold schoolboy Thomas Devlin was
OL,8,Fmurdered in a sectarian attack in 2005.
OL,10,FHe said: "I just bounced from one call
OL,11,Fto the next to the next, doesn't
OL,12,Fmatter how horrific you just got on
OL,13,Fwith it.
OL,15,F"I have my name written on the walls
OL,16,Fin certain estates because I was black
OL,17,Fand white with the crime.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
