OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,FUTV can reveal the number of officers
OL,7,Fwho have taken ill-health retirement
OL,8,Fhas soared in the last two years.
OL,10,FThe total number rose by a staggering
OL,11,F140% from 83 in 2023 to 200 in 2024.
OL,13,FA figure that is three times higher
OL,14,Fthan in England and Wales.
OL,16,FPolice echoed the urgency of this
OL,17,Fissue during a recent Policing Board
OL,18,Fmeeting.
