OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,FClaire Duffield, the PSNI's Assistant
OL,7,FChief Officer added: ''Some of the
OL,8,Froles that our officers do expose them
OL,9,Fto greater trauma than others.
OL,11,F"For example, we know that we have
OL,12,Fpolice staff and officers that do very
OL,13,Fspecialist work in our public
OL,14,Fprotection branch, in our collision
OL,15,Finvestigation unit in the child
OL,16,Finternet protection team and they have
OL,17,Fmuch more regular exposure to
OL,18,Ftraumatic incidents or material.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
