OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,F"Now we are focusing our resources to
OL,7,Fhelp and support, and we also know we
OL,8,Fhave to be careful about the tenure of
OL,9,Fpeople in those roles.''
OL,11,FThe retirement figures equate a
OL,12,Fsignificant loss of experience from
OL,13,Fareas of policing such as crime and
OL,14,Fpublic protection.
OL,16,FUTV understands that among those who
OL,17,Fhave taken ill health retirement are
OL,18,Fofficers who worked on the Alexander
OL,19,FMcCartney case.
