OL,3,C'The job took a part of me': The
OL,4,Ctrauma of serving on the thin blue line
OL,6,FHe's the Catfish from Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fwho abused thousands of children
OL,8,Fonline and drove one teenager to take
OL,9,Fher own life.
OL,11,FIt was a harrowing and traumatic case
OL,12,Ffor detectives to work on.
OL,14,FThe sectarian murder of schoolboy
OL,15,FThomas Devlin in 2005 in North Belfast
OL,16,Fstill haunts the officer who spent two
OL,17,Fdecades on the frontline in the city.
